<plot>How to show the long term effect of climate changes in 7 minutes? With the help of simple metaphor. Imagine a fridge full of food. What would happen inside, when someone forgets to close the door? Even small child can understand it. The Fridge is short metaphoric story about one fridge, one man, and three careless chicken.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?328227</url></doc>
